OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776250558
OL,3,CUK outlook darkens as IMF warns Iran
OL,4,Cwar could trigger global recession
OL,6,FForecasting, as they say, is a mug's
OL,7,Fgame. Quite right too.
OL,9,FThe one thing you can be confident of
OL,10,Fwhen you look at the International
OL,11,FMonetary Fund's latest set of numbers
OL,12,Fis that they almost certainly won't
OL,13,Fcome to pass - not in the seemingly
OL,14,Fprecise way they are laid out, anyway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776250558
OL,3,CUK outlook darkens as IMF warns Iran
OL,4,Cwar could trigger global recession
OL,6,FBut they still have value, and are
OL,7,Fperhaps best seen as economic "vibes"
OL,8,F- an informed guess about which
OL,9,Fcountries are most exposed to the war
OL,10,Fin the Gulf, as the ongoing closure of
OL,11,Fthe Strait of Hormuz threatens to
OL,12,Fthrow the world economy "off course".
OL,14,FThe UK is perceived as being
OL,15,Fvulnerable.
OL,17,FThe IMF has cut its forecast for
OL,18,Feconomic growth this year to 0.8% -
OL,19,Fthe largest downgrade among the G7's
OL,20,Fwealthy nations - before improving to
OL,21,F1.3% in 2027.
OL,26,@oD@_OUoD@eO]tD@YOUtD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776250558
OL,3,CUK outlook darkens as IMF warns Iran
OL,4,Cwar could trigger global recession
OL,6,FInflation, which had been gently
OL,7,Ffading before the US and Israel
OL,8,Fattacked Iran, is now expected to edge
OL,9,Fup again, as is the rate of
OL,10,Funemployment, which is predicted to
OL,11,Freach 5.6%.
OL,13,FHigher prices and more jobseekers will
OL,14,Fleave everyone - households,
OL,15,Fbusinesses and the government -
OL,16,Fpoorer. But an average inflation rate
OL,17,Fof 3.2% in 2026 is a far cry from the
OL,18,Fdouble-digit inflation the UK
OL,19,Fexperienced the last time energy
OL,20,Fprices took off, after Russia invaded
OL,21,FUkraine four years ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776250558
OL,3,CUK outlook darkens as IMF warns Iran
OL,4,Cwar could trigger global recession
OL,6,FThe IMF's assumption is that the scale
OL,7,Fof this shock is not comparable, and
OL,8,Fthat the war will be short-lived. But
OL,9,Fits forecast was effectively nailed
OL,10,Fdown a month ago. Energy prices have
OL,11,Frisen since, and what happens next
OL,12,Flooks as unpredictable as the man
OL,13,Fdriving events - President Trump.
OL,15,FOil and gas remain the lifeblood of
OL,16,Fthe world economy, and there is "the
OL,17,Fprospect of a major energy crisis
OL,18,Fshould hostilities continue," as
OL,19,FPierre-Olivier Gourinchas, the IMF's
OL,20,Feconomic counsellor, puts it.
OL,26,@xD@aOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776250558
OL,3,CUK outlook darkens as IMF warns Iran
OL,4,Cwar could trigger global recession
OL,6,FIf the Strait remains blocked for
OL,7,Fmonths and oil hovers at around $110
OL,8,Fthis year and $120 next, then the
OL,9,FIMF's "severe scenario" comes into
OL,10,Fplay - and a global recession becomes
OL,11,Fa "close call".
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@qD@GOUqD@WO]sD@COUsD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
