OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776250558
OL,3,CUK outlook darkens as IMF warns Iran
OL,4,Cwar could trigger global recession
OL,6,F"If I subsidise your energy bill this
OL,7,Fyear and then put up your taxes next
OL,8,Fyear to pay for it, are you really
OL,9,Fbetter off? I would argue not," says a
OL,10,Fgovernment source.
OL,12,FAs the chancellor wrestles with how
OL,13,Fbest to protect living standards while
OL,14,Fstaying within her self-imposed rules
OL,15,Fon debt and borrowing, what's clear is
OL,16,Fthat - even if the war were to end
OL,17,Ftomorrow- a squeeze is coming.
OL,19,FThe RAC thinks pump prices have
OL,20,Fprobably peaked for the time being,
OL,21,Fbut they were just the beginning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776250558
OL,3,CUK outlook darkens as IMF warns Iran
OL,4,Cwar could trigger global recession
OL,6,FFood prices are likely to start edging
OL,7,Fup in the months ahead. A shortage of
OL,8,Fjet fuel looks set to hit air travel
OL,9,Fand tourism this summer.
OL,11,FAnd mortgage rates have surged -
OL,12,Fpulling money out of the pockets of
OL,13,Fhundreds of thousands of homeowners as
OL,14,Fthey refinance.
OL,16,FThe IMF's "benign" assumption has GDP
OL,17,Fper capita in the UK, a pretty good
OL,18,Fproxy for living standards, rising by
OL,19,Fjust 0.3% this year - the lowest
OL,20,Fincrease in the G7.
OL,26,@xD@KOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
